name: Money Clip for Women
description:
Hey ladies, have you ever used a money clip. Great for just slipping in your pocket or instead of fumbling with your wallet, just slide into one of compartments of your purse for quick access.

Here is an new old stock brass money clip that I have etched with a simple and pretty leaf vine design with a subtle green patina added to the leaves.

The money clip measures 2" X 1"

Etching produces unique results and may vary slightly from one pictured.

name: Beware Money Clip
description:
Rustic and distressed Gothic/Steampunk style money clip for men, or a woman with attitude. 

Etched on a new old stock brass money clip is the word "BEWARE" and along with a rough texture of fingerprints, slashes and dings, no one will dare to mess with your money!

Measures 1" X 2"

Etching produces unique results and may vary slightly from one pictured.

name: Poison Money Clip
description:
Rustic and distressed brass money clip, etched and creepily textured, oxidized with a worn finish for an old world look. Perfect accessory for any man or woman with attitude. 

Measures 2" X 1"

Poison - Be Careful

An antique pocket watch design has been etched into the new old stock brass money clip and embellished with moveable metal watch hands for a 3d look. Hand applied patina added to give it an old world, been around a while look. Measures 1" X 2"
